'''大眼赤刀魚'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Cepola macrophthalma''）是一種[[赤刀魚屬|赤刀魚屬]]。牠們分佈在由[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]北至[[挪威|挪威]]的東[[大西洋|大西洋]]及[[地中海|地中海]]。<ref name=Base>{{FishBase species | genus = Cepola  | species = '''macrophthalma | month = November | year = 2009}}</ref>'''

==分佈==
大眼赤刀魚分佈在由[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]北部至[[挪威|挪威]]東[[大西洋|大西洋]]，與及[[愛琴海|愛琴海]]及[[尼羅河三角洲|尼羅河三角洲]]以西[[地中海|地中海]]的海岸及[[大陸棚|大陸棚]]。<ref name=Base/>牠們棲息在沙質及泥質海床，深度介乎10-400米的水域。<ref name=Base/><ref name=burrow>{{Cite web|last=Reebs|first=Stéphan G|title=Can fishes build things?|work=howfishbehave.ca|date=2008|url=http://www.howfishbehave.ca/pdf/can%20fish%20build%20things.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2009-11-19|archive-date=2011-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706182813/http://www.howfishbehave.ca/pdf/can%20fish%20build%20things.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==特徵==
大眼赤刀魚的身體很幼，尤如絲帶一般，尾巴部份逐漸收窄。牠們呈紅色，底部呈橙色或黃色。牠們的[[眼睛|眼睛]]很大，呈銀色。[[背鰭|背鰭]]及[[臀鰭|臀鰭]]一直沿身體延至尾巴，與尾鰭連合。牠們有很大的口，可以張開至[[銳角|銳角]]的角度；[[牙齒|牙齒]]很幼，排列得很疏。<ref name=Base/>

大眼赤刀魚的長度可以很不同，平均也有40厘米。最長的紀錄為80厘米。<ref name=Base/>牠們的背鰭有67-70條軟鰭條，臀鰭有60條。背部鰭條沒有分隔，尾鰭的中央鰭條很長。<ref name=Base/>

==生態及行為==
在發現大眼赤刀魚群落前，對其所知甚少。自從在[[英國|英國]][[德文郡|德文郡]]對出的[[蘭迪島|蘭迪島]]發現牠們的群落後，就進行多個研究，並且也有進行飼養。<ref name=Atkinson/>蘭迪島群落的數量曾經達14000條，但卻嚴重下降，現已有措施禁止漁獵。<ref name=SOS>{{Cite news|last=Pope|first=Frank|title=Lundy's S.O.S: a blueprint for sustainable fishing?|newspaper=The Times|date=6 December 2008|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/environment/article5251791.ece|accessdate=2009-11-21}}</ref><ref name=BBCDevon>{{Cite web|title=Getting a close-up look of Lundy's sealife|work=Where I Live: Devon|publisher=BBC News|date=9 October 2003|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/devon/outdoors/nature/2003/lundy_undersea.shtml|accessdate=2009-11-12|archive-date=2011-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111022233958/http://www.bbc.co.uk/devon/outdoors/nature/2003/lundy_undersea.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大眼赤刀魚是會挖穴的，主要吃[[多椎異康吉鰻|多椎異康吉鰻]]，並會留在洞穴捕食[[浮游動物|浮游動物]]。牠們不會像多椎異康吉鰻般固定在洞穴，而是可以自由來往洞穴。<ref name=burrow/>大眼赤刀魚的洞穴入口呈漏斗形，洞深達1米，平均深49厘米。<ref name=Atkinson/>牠們會在[[黎明|黎明]]或[[黃昏|黃昏]]時份挖穴，以其口挖開泥土，再用身體推開。牠們挖穴時會造成約3升的泥濘及沙土，挖穴時間約要6小時。<ref name=Atkinson>{{Cite journal en|last=Atkinson|first=R. J. A.|coauthors=Pullin, R. S.|title=Observations on the Burrows and Burrowing Behaviour of the Red Band-Fish, ''Cepola rubescens'' L.|journal=Marine Ecology|volume=17|issue=1-3|pages=23-40|date=1996|doi=10.1111/j.1439-0485.1996.tb00487.x|accessdate=2009-11-03}}</ref><ref name=burrow/>牠們的洞穴很多會與其他挖穴的[[魚類|魚類]]及[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]的洞穴相連，而且都是故意的。<ref>{{Cite web|last=United Kingdom Marine Special Areas of Conservation|title=Interactions between megafaunal burrowers|work=Community ecology: interactions between species|url=http://www.ukmarinesac.org.uk/communities/seapens/sp3_2.htm|accessdate=2009-11-22|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201120255/http://www.ukmarinesac.org.uk/communities/seapens/sp3_2.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大眼赤刀魚是其他[[海洋|海洋]][[掠食者|掠食者]]的主要獵物，如[[海魴|海魴]]<ref>{{Cite journal en|last=Stergiou|first=K. I.|coauthors=Fourtouni, H.|title=Food habits, ontogenetic diet shift and selectivity in ''Zeus faber'' Linnaeus, 1758|journal=Journal of Fish Biology|volume=39|pages=589-603|date=1991|url=http://ichthyology.bio.auth.gr/files/stergiou/B/B11.pdf|accessdate=2009-11-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721074710/http://ichthyology.bio.auth.gr/files/stergiou/B/B11.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-21}}</ref>、[[海豚屬|海豚屬]]<ref>{{Cite journal en|last=Silva|first=M. A.|title=Diet of common dolphins, ''Delphinus delphis'', off the Portuguese continental coast|journal=Journal of the Marine Biology Association of the United Kingdom|volume=79|pages=531-530|date=1999|url=http://www.horta.uac.pt/projectos/cetamarh/Artigos/artigo4.pdf|doi=10.1017/S0025315498000654|accessdate=2009-11-03|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927152530/http://www.horta.uac.pt/projectos/cetamarh/Artigos/artigo4.pdf|archive-date=2011-09-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>及[[八爪魚|八爪魚]]。<ref>{{Cite journal en|last=Şen|first=Halil|title=Food Preference of ''Eledone moschata'' Lamarck, 1799 (Cephalopoda: Octopodidae) in Captive Conditions|journal=International Journal of Natural and Engineering Sciences|volume=1|issue=2|pages=29-31|date=2007|url=http://www.nobelonline.net/UserFiles/File/4hsen.pdf|accessdate=2009-11-22}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>大眼赤刀魚挖洞及吃浮游動物的[[生態位|生態位]]可能是因被掠食的壓力所造成的。<ref>{{Cite journal en|last=Stergiou|first=K. I.|title=Abundance-depth relationship, condition factor, and adaptive value of zooplanktonophagy for red bandfish, ''Cepola macrophthalma''|journal=Journal of Fish Biology|volume=42|pages=645-60|date=1993|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1439-0426.2007.01047.x|doi=10.1111/j.1439-0426.2007.01047.x|accessdate=2009-11-20}}</ref>

==食用==
傳統上，大眼赤刀魚都是重要的食物。早於前5世紀[[希臘|希臘]]的[[麦瑟库斯|麦瑟库斯]]（Mithaecus）就已經會煮食大眼赤刀魚。<ref>{{Cite book en|last=Dalby|first=Andrew|title=Siren Feasts|publisher=Routledge|date=1996|location=Abingdon, Oxfordshire, England|pages=109-10|id=ISBN 0-41515657-2}}</ref>他紀錄處理大眼赤刀魚的方法：取出內臟，棄掉頭部，沖洗及切片；加入[[芝士|芝士]]及[[橄欖油|橄欖油]]。<ref name=Food>{{Cite book en|last =Dalby|first=Andrew|title=Food in the ancient world from A to Z|publisher=Routledge|date=2003|location=Abingdon, Oxfordshire, England|pages=79, 220|id=ISBN 0-41523259-7}}</ref>現今牠們已不再如以往般重要。在一些國家，如[[義大利|義大利]]及[[西班牙|西班牙]]仍會食用大眼赤刀魚，而其他的國家的漁民則很多時會將之放回海上。<ref>{{Cite journal en|last=Stergiou|first=K. I.|coauthors=Economidis, P.; and Sinis, A.|title=Age, growth, and mortality of red bandfish, ''Cepola macrophthalma'' (L.), in the western Aegean Sea (Greece)|journal=Journal of Fish Biology|volume=40|issue=3|pages=395-418|date=1992|doi=10.1111/j.1095-8649.1992.tb02586.x|accessdate=2009-10-20}}</ref>

